subject: Football
lead_paragraph: For the Jets, Miami, hapless on offense and defense, proved to be the antidote to their recent struggles as they make their playoff push. In sweeping the season series against the Dolphins for the first time in eight years, the Jets bolstered their hopes of making the playoffs.
